docs {
  Create or update an A1 policy via A1PMS.
  - ric_id: target Near-RT RIC
  - policy_id: unique ID for this policy
  - service_id: must be a registered service
  - policytype_id: empty for default type, or specific type ID
  - policy_data: JSON policy content (schema depends on policy type)
  Note: Requires a policy type to be registered on the RIC (via an xApp).
        Currently no policy types are available, so this will return an error.
}
